mical reactions driven by extreme heat. In today\u0027s image, Bláhver, a natural hot spring, dazzles in electric blue. Its color comes from mineral- and silica-rich waters that reflect light on the surface.","Image":{"Url":"/th?id=OHR.SpringIceland_EN-US6846318257_1920x1080.webp","Wallpaper":"/th?id=OHR.SpringIceland_EN-US6846318257_1920x1200.jpg\u0026rf=LaDigue_1920x1200.jpg","Downloadable":true},"Headline":"Fire under frost","Title":"Geothermal blue pool Bláhver at Hveravellir, Iceland","Copyright":"© Juan Maria Coy Vergara/Getty Images","SocialGood":null,"MapLink":{"Url":"//platform.bing.com/geo/REST/v1/Imagery/Map/RoadVibrant/64.865398,-19.559103/7?key=AsSOKo7OOz5VAtfAj0rjgaXlhCrCZI6PGbLj7GCH8IW2HUalyg4BVhqA0z77PRCj\u0026c=en-US\u0026od=2\u0026shading=flat\u0026pp=64.865398,-19.559103;S9;Hveravellir, Iceland\u0026st=pp|v:false;lv:false_trs|v:false;lv:false\u0026ml=Basemap,Landmarks\u0026logo=no\u0026mapSize=386,434\u0026da=ro","Link":""},"QuickFact":{"MainText":"","LinkUrl":"","LinkText":""},"TriviaUrl":"/search?q=Bing+homepage+quiz\u0026filters=WQOskey:\u0022HPQuiz_20260310_SpringIceland\u0022\u0026FORM=HPQUIZ","BackstageUrl":"/search?q=Blahver+pool+Iceland\u0026form=hpcapt\u0026filters=HpDate:\u002220260310_0700\u0022+mgzv3configlist:\u0022BingQA_Encyclopedia_Layout\u0022","TriviaId":"HPQuiz_20260310_SpringIceland"},"Ssd":"20260310","Name":"SpringIceland","Market":"EN-US","Hash":"6846318257","FullDateString":"Mar 10, 2026"}],"PreloadMediaContents":[],"LocStrings":{"LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_IOTD":"Image of the day","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_IOTD_LEARN_MORE":"Learn more","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_DONATE_NOW":"Donate now","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_FACT":"Quick fact:","LOC_HOMEPAGE_GALLERY_CARD_TITLE":"Recent Homepage images","LOC_HOMEPAGE_VERTICAL_SCROLL_GALLERY_IMAGE_ARIALABEL":"Homepage image for {0}","LOC_HOMEPAGE_ON_THIS_DAY_TITLE":"On this day in history","LOC_HOMEPAGE_ON_THIS_DAY_IMAGE_ARIALABEL":"On this day in {0}, {1}","LOC_HOMEPAGE_SHAR